
'''''Zinabu'''''  ni filime yo muri [[Gana]] yo mu 1987 iyobowe na William Akuffo na Richard Quartey<ref>https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/Zinabu-the-first-Ghanaian-film-to-be-shot-using-a-video-camera-827290</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Zinabu avuga amateka ''y'umupfumu winjiye mu bukristo.''<ref>https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/Zinabu-the-first-Ghanaian-film-to-be-shot-using-a-video-camera-827290?gallery=1</ref> 

== Umusaruro ==
Filime yafashwe mu 1985 ikoresheje kamera ya videwo, aho kuba kamera ya firime<ref>https://ghanaianmuseum.com/tag/william-akuffo/</ref> . Video yari igikoresho gishya muri kiriya gihe, ariko Akuffo yamenye ibyiza amashusho ya videwo yari afite kuri firime, kubera ko selile  yari ihenze kandi itanga imbogamizi zo kuyikwirakwiza<ref>https://www.ohioswallow.com/extras/9780896802865_toc_introduction.pdf</ref>. ''Zinabu'' yabaye firime ya mbere yo muri Gana yakozwe kuri videwo<ref>https://www.sahistory.org.za/article/ghallywood-evolution-ghanas-film-industry</ref>. 

== Ikwirakwizwa ==
Mu gihe cyo gutunganya ''Zinabu'', guverinoma ya [[Gana]] yashyizeho itegeko ribuza kureba amashusho, mu rwego rwo gukumira ingaruka mbi batekerezaga ko filime z’Abanyamerika n’Ubushinwa zitabifitiye uruhushya zigira ku muco wa [[Gana]]<ref>https://marginalia.lareviewofbooks.org/witches-holy-spirit-christian-film-production-ghana-katrien-pype/</ref>. Iri tegeko ryakuweho mu 1987, ahanini bitewe nakazi ka Akuffo. Filime yakiriye bwa mbere muri Globe Cinema. Kwerekanwa byari bigamije kwigana firime isanzwe: umukinnyi wa videwo ntabwo yabonaga abari aho, kandi Akuffo yari mucyumba cyo kwerekana<ref>https://www.culturalencyclopaedia.org/african-video-movies-and-global-desires.a-ghanaian-history-article</ref>. 

== Umurage ==
''Zinabu'' nicyo kintu cya mbere cyerekana amashusho yo muri [[Gana]], gitangira uburyo bushya bwo gutunganya amafilime kavukire yakura mu ntangiriro ya za 90. Mu 1988, hasohotse filime ebyiri za videwo, ariko iyi zigera kuri zirindwi mu 1991, zirenga 50 muri 1993.  Akuffo yakoze kandi ibisobanuro bitatu kuri ''Zinabu''<ref>https://www.ghgossip.com/5-timeless-ghanaian-movies-you-probably-havent-seen-before/</ref> <ref>https://www.nova-cinema.org/prog/2003/409/africa-films/</ref>. 

